Load and join files function :¶

In [2]:
def load_join(path,fs,ls):
    d = pd.read_csv(path+str(fs)+".csv",encoding = "ISO-8859-1")
    for i in range(fs+1,ls):
        d = d.append(pd.read_csv(path+str(i)+".csv",encoding = "ISO-8859-1"))
    return d
